--------------
- PyMythTvFs -
--------------

Python and Fuse based file system for accessing MythTV recordings.

Usage:
------

Run 'pymythtvfs' providing a directory to mount the file system at as a 
parameter.

To unmount use 'fusermount -u <mount point>'.

